$Id$

The structure for the documentation is as follows:

- README: this document
- api.txt: description of function calls available to an application
  programmer
- design.txt: some musings on the design process of the library
- mechanism: a description on how the internals of the library interact
- integration.txt: a discussion on the integration of the library into a
  larger project

Software related documents:

- sllist-tests.txt: software specification and test definition for a
  singly linked list

